  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Dana Wallet和Blindbit Oracle之间的交互流程。核心场景是轻钱包如何在不下载完整区块的情况下获取UTXO信息。Dana Wallet作为Scanner角色，首先要向Blindbit Oracle订阅新区块通知。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dana Wallet",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "Scanner",
        "subscribe new blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那Bitcoin Core Node在这里是什么位置？是Oracle主动去取数据，还是Core推送过来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bitcoin Core Node",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "New Block"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Core是推送机制。当Bitcoin Core Node产生新区块时，会主动发给Blindbit-Oracle。然后Oracle内部要做三件事：计算tweak、索引未花费输出、构建taproot GCS filter。这些我打算用Note标注在Oracle右侧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bitcoin Core Node",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "New Block",
        "compute tweak",
        "index unspent outputs",
        "build taproot GCS filter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础骨架画出来：Scanner订阅BP，BC推送新区块给BP，BP内部三个处理步骤。不过我看到您提到\"compute tweak\"和\"compute spent\"，这两个都是Oracle内部消息吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scanner",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "Bitcoin Core Node",
        "compute tweak",
        "compute spent"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "\"compute spent\"这个表述不对，应该是\"build taproot GCS filter\"之后，Oracle才把新区块通知给Scanner。另外Oracle内部还有个自循环：compute tweak之后要再算一次tweak用于spent检测，然后才是build filter。让我重新理一下：BP收到新区块后，内部依次做compute tweak、index unspent、再compute tweak、compute spent、最后build filter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "compute tweak",
        "index unspent outputs",
        "compute spent",
        "build taproot GCS filter",
        "new block",
        "Scanner"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，Oracle内部是五步处理，然后推送给Scanner。接下来Scanner收到新区块后，会主动请求tweaks和UTXOs对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scanner",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "Request tweaks & UTXOs for block"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，但这里有个安全细节：Scanner的请求需要经过Security Firewall验证。所以消息上要标注这个上下文。Oracle返回Tweaks和相关的UTXOs之后，Scanner还会再请求filters。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scanner",
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "Request tweaks & UTXOs for block",
        "Security_Firewall",
        "Tweaks & relevant UTXOs",
        "Request filters"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后一步是Scanner本地计算UTXOs？还是Oracle返回utxo和outpoint filters之后Scanner再算？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scanner",
        "utxo and outpoint filters",
        "calculate UTXOs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "后者。Oracle返回utxo和outpoint filters，然后Scanner本地做calculate UTXOs。这样整个流程闭环：订阅→推送→内部处理→双向请求→本地计算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blindbit-Oracle",
        "Scanner",
        "utxo and outpoint filters",
        "calculate UTXOs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我检查一遍：Scanner订阅BP，BC推新区块给BP，BP五步内部处理，BP推新区块给Scanner，Scanner经防火墙请求tweaks/UTXOs，BP返回，Scanner请求filters，BP返回utxo和outpoint filters，Scanner本地计算。所有消息流向和参与者都对应上了。",
